  "text": "The slave control block allows to compute the set-point velocity V s of the nanostage, which is also sent back to the homothetic coupling block to be used in the master control. The calculation of V s is based on the comparison of the master force translated in the micro world F micro , and the cantilever contact force F canti as in [CITATION_1] . As the nanostage is controlled on position, P s is computed by integrating V s with saturation levels at 0 and 12.10 −6 m, travel limits of the nanostage.",
